SIMPLE: unskillful
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unskillful
<hw>Un*skill"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Spelt also
<ets>unskilful</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Not skillful; inexperienced; awkward; bungling;
<as>as, an <ex>unskillful</ex> surgeon or mechanic; an
<ex>unskillful</ex> logician</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Lacking discernment; injudicious;
ignorant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Though it make the <qex>unskillful</qex> laugh, can not but make
the judicious grieve.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*skill"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*skill"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unslacked</ent>⟦br⟧
